六国橄榄球支持者可能以 9 亿英镑收购《Runescape》开发商 Jagex https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/six-nations-rugby-backers-could-acquire-runescape-developers-jagex-for-900million-3583970?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=six-nations-橄榄球支持者可以以 9 亿美元收购 runescape 开发商 jagexAli Shutler Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:21:52 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3583970 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="符文景观死灵术。信用：Jagex。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> CVC Capital Partners 还管理 RAC 以及各种制药和科技公司</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/six-nations-rugby-backers-could-acquire-runescape-developers-jagex-for-900million-3583970">六国橄榄球支持者可能以 9 亿英镑收购《Runescape》开发商 Jagex 的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="符文景观死灵术。信用：Jagex。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/runescape-necromancy-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/jagex">Jagex</a>是大型多人在线角色扮演游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/runescape">Runescape</a>的开发商，可能会被私募股权公司以 9 亿英镑收购。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/with-fresh-start-worlds-runescape-is-reaching-a-new-generation-3350832">随着全新的开始世界，“RuneScape”正在走向新一代</a></strong></li></ul><p>凯雷集团自 2021 年 1 月以来一直拥有这家位于剑桥的开发商，但据<a href="https://news.sky.com/story/six-nations-backer-cvc-in-talks-to-buy-runescape-maker-for-900m-13065234?sv1=affiliate&amp;sv_campaign_id=103504&amp;awc=11005_1707316166_6bbc0d2ef232fafc0993ff6e27e289c2&amp;dcmp=afc-103504-na-na-longtail&amp;dclid=CJj_96y4mYQDFeJC9ggd6RkIVA" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>天空新闻报道</em></a>，CVC Capital Partners 正在寻求收购该工作室，以收购更多拥有强大国际用户群的公司。</p><p> CVC Capital Partners 是一家总部位于卢森堡的“全球领先的另类投资管理公司”。他们拥有价值超过 1420 亿英镑的<a href="https://www.cvc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">投资组合</a>，涵盖从豪华游艇到药品的各个领域。他们拥有西班牙西甲足球联赛、英国橄榄球联赛以及年度六国橄榄球锦标赛，此外还拥有故障公司 RAC 和送货服务 Hermes。</p><p>报道称，“市政府消息人士称，CVC 已经击败了 Jagex 的众多竞争对手，并可能在几天内签署正式协议，购买该公司的控股权。”该报道从去年开始就收购进行讨论。</p><p>据称，凯雷集团希望以 10 亿英镑的价格出售，但许多投资者对 Jagex 的商业计划和开发渠道表示怀疑。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="家庭 - RuneScape 官方原声带" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BkzRZ8_fsIg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>如果收购顺利进行，CVC 将成为过去十年中第四家收购 Jagex 的公司。上海虹投最初于 2016 年收购了该公司，然后于 2020 年以 4.19 亿英镑的价格将其出售给麦克阿瑟财富控股公司。凯雷集团于次年收购了它，收购金额未公开。据<em><a href="https://www.ft.com/content/fbd6537c-ece4-493a-9d23-33e428282e05" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国《金融时报》</a></em>报道，Jagex 报告 2021 年营收为 1.25 亿英镑，利润为 3700 万英镑。</p><p>凯雷投资集团、CVC 或 Jagex 均未对此次潜在收购发表评论。</p><p> 2022 年，Jagex 宣布将开发<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/jagex-is-making-an-open-world-survival-game-set-in-runescape-universe-3254915">一款以 Runescape 宇宙为背景、基于虚幻引擎 5 构建的开放世界生存游戏</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/old-school-runescape">Old School Runescape</a>目前正在准备进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/old-school-runescape-to-get-hd-update-3576954">大规模高清更新。</a></p><p>在其他消息中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy">《最终幻想》</a></em>系列制作人北濑佳典表示，他想重制<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7"><em>《最终幻想 7》</em></a> ，以避免它成为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/square-enix-remade-final-fantasy-7-to-stop-it-being-that-game-my-dad-played-3583958">我爸爸玩的那个游戏</a>”。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/six-nations-rugby-backers-could-acquire-runescape-developers-jagex-for-900million-3583970">六国橄榄球支持者可能以 9 亿英镑收购《Runescape》开发商 Jagex 的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
